Nine spell slots just seems like an odd number to me. I also think they should add 2 more, 10 would be good number.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>I've heard people say stuff like this before... where do you get this impression after what, 5 years?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
You have a really good point here. But it always did crack me up how sometimes contrived things seem. You know, leveling a character up to a point where they can traverse the alternate planes of existence, kill gods and even conquer time itself... but you still miss notes like a complete noob. Eight spell slots seems like one of those things to me hehe.<br>
<br>
<br>
So yeah, I really want 10 spell slots. But either way I'm really looking forward to this next expansion. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=772824"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.comcast.net/~toccard/Yuma.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
